title: Carb Articles From About_com.pdf
description:
Articles compiled from About.com and other sources regarding Carbohydrates and a review of The Low Carbohydrate Atkins diet for Diabetics [and pre-diabetics].  

Information on carbohydrates has changed dramatically in the past 20 years.  Genetics is a component for those sensitive to carbohydrates.  

If you are interested in nutrition this is a must read.
